<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Your SmartTrip Verification Code</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    background: #f0e8d8;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }
  .wrapper {
    max-width: 580px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    background: #ffffff;
  }
  /* Header */
  .header {
    background: #0d0d0d;
    padding: 36px 40px 30px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8a6e2a, #b8963e, #d4b06a, #b8963e, #8a6e2a);
  }
  .logo {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  .logo span { color: #d4b06a; font-style: italic; }
  .header-sub {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(212,176,106,0.6);
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  /* Body */
  .body { padding: 44px 40px 36px; }

  .greeting {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #0d0d0d;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .greeting em { font-style: italic; color: #b8963e; }

  .message {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #6b6560;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  /* OTP box */
  .otp-section {
    background: #faf6ef;
    border: 1px solid rgba(184,150,62,0.25);
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .otp-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #b8963e;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .otp-label::before,
  .otp-label::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 0.5px;
    background: rgba(184,150,62,0.3);
    max-width: 60px;
  }
  .otp-digits {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .otp-digit {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 52px;
    height: 62px;
    line-height: 62px;
    text-align: center;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(184,150,62,0.4);
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #0d0d0d;
  }
  .otp-expires {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #6b6560;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .otp-expires strong { color: #b8963e; }

  /* Warning */
  .warning {
    background: rgba(192,57,43,0.06);
    border-left: 3px solid #c0392b;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .warning p {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: #6b6560;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .warning strong { color: #c0392b; }

  /* Divider */
  .divider {
    height: 0.5px;
    background: rgba(184,150,62,0.2);
    margin: 28px 0;
  }

  .closing {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: #6b6560;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .signature {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #0d0d0d;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .signature span { color: #b8963e; font-style: italic; }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    background: #0d0d0d;
    padding: 22px 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .footer p {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(240,232,216,0.35);
    line-height: 1.6;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .footer a { color: rgba(212,176,106,0.5); text-decoration: none; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">Smart<span>Trip</span></div>
    <div class="header-sub">Luxury Travel Collection</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Body -->
  <div class="body">

    <div class="greeting">
      Hello, <em>{{ user.fullName }}</em>
    </div>

    <p class="message">
      We received a request to reset the password for your SmartTrip account
      linked to <strong style="color:#0d0d0d;">{{ user.email }}</strong>.<br><br>
      Use the verification code below to complete your password reset.
      This code is valid for <strong style="color:#0d0d0d;">10 minutes</strong>.
    </p>

    <!-- OTP Box -->
    <div class="otp-section">
      <div class="otp-label">Verification Code</div>
      <div class="otp-digits">
        {% for digit in otp|split('') %}
        <span class="otp-digit">{{ digit }}</span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div class="otp-expires">
        Expires in <strong>10 minutes</strong> &nbsp;·&nbsp; Do not share this code
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Security Warning -->
    <div class="warning">
      <p>
        <strong>Didn't request this?</strong> If you did not request a password reset,
        you can safely ignore this email. Your account remains secure and no changes
        have been made.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <p class="closing">
      For your security, this code will expire in 10 minutes and can only be used once.
      If you need a new code, simply go back and request another one.
    </p>

    <div class="signature">
      Warm regards,<br>
      The <span>SmartTrip</span> Team
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <div class="footer">
    <p>
      © {{ "now"|date("Y") }} SmartTrip. All rights reserved.<br>
      This is an automated message — please do not reply directly to this email.<br>
      <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="#">Terms of Service</a>
    </p>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
